              "free_text": [
                " 54 He-3 filled counters were mounted around the",
                "focal-plane detector chamber of the VASSILISSA,",
                "in three concentric rings, covered by organic glass",
                "and boron polyethylene, both of 5 cm in thickness.",
                " Efficiency of detection of neutron measured using",
                " chamber with Cm-248 source and Si detector (1 cm**2",
                " pin-diode), placed in the position of the focal-plane",
                " semiconductor detector, was 36+-1 %."
              ]
            }
          ],
